##### GUI #####
o		toggle osd information, off, elapsed, elapsed/total

arrow keys	left-right: 10 sec, up-down: 1 min

pgup pgdown	10 min

[ ]  		playback speed 10%

{ }		half/double speed

backspace	reset speed to normal

s		take screenshot

S		start/stop taking screenshots



extract frames from part of video
$ mplayer samba.mp4 -ss 00:00:15 -endpos 5 -ao null -vo jpeg

extract and recode part of video
$ mencoder -ss 00:30:00 -endpos 00:00:05 -oac copy -ovc copy originalfile -o newfile

